# iReview — AI-to-AI Code Review

To review code changes, run:
```bash
bash scripts/ireview.sh review
```

Arguments: --base main | --full | --adversarial | specific files
Cancel: bash scripts/ireview.sh cancel
Status: bash scripts/ireview.sh status

Config: .ireview.json (copy from .ireview.example.json)
Protocol: skills/ireview/SKILL.md
